    dc:description "FIGURES 29–32. Female genitalia of Endotricha spp. 29, Uttarakhand, Chakrata (13255/H10); 30, Sikkim, Golitar (8770/ H10); 31, Sikkim, Golitar (13264/H10); 32, Sikkim, Dodak (8839/H10)." ;
